Text: Who are you...?!
*gasp*
//カットシーン再生
Huff...huff...!
Lady Alpha!
Wh-What was that just now...?!
An afterimage left by the speed of her approach...!
...Epsilon! Zeta!
Hah!
Damn you!
What the hell...?!
She dodged everything...while only barely moving?!

No way...! She instantly read my magic-infused
slashes?!
G-Grrrrrr... Grrrr....!!!
She must be an incredible dark knight...!

I'm not scared, I'm not scared... Gotta stay
strong... Gotta stay strong...!!!

Delta, calm yourself! Don't go charging in
heedlessly—
Ungh...!
Lady Alpha!!!
She...stopped?
Don't let your guard down!
Grr... If you're gonna attack, then just do it!!!
...I have an idea.
Eta?!
What in the world are you—
...I'm going to try approaching her with slime...

...I knew it. She attacks unconditionally...if
anything comes close enough.

So...she won't do anything as long as we stay away
from her?

I suppose that makes her like some sort of
gatekeeper...

...If she won't come after us any further, then let's
pull out and return to Alexandria.
But Lady Alpha...

I'm not happy about it either, but as things stand,
we aren't strong enough to overcome this elven
swordswoman.

Even if we attacked her in unison, the attempt would
cost us our lives if she retaliates with irresistible
force.

...A hard but accurate pill to swallow. I agree with
Lady Alpha.
B-But...! I'm not...scared... Grrr...!

The way your tail's all curled between your legs says
otherwise. Natural instincts never lie.

And fleabag here isn't the only one... Every beastly
fiber of my being is telling me I shouldn't stay here!

Let's come back again...after searching elsewhere
for leads. There's still plenty of interesting things
out there... Hehehe.

I'll take the rear, just in case something happens.
The rest of you, withdraw at once!
Understood!
Copy that!
A swordswoman that resembles me... It can't be!
